#. type: textblock
#: ../align/virt-alignment-scan.pod:73
msgid ""
"When listing all libvirt domains (no I<-a> or I<-d> option given) this "
"column is prefixed by the libvirt name or UUID (if I<--uuid> is given).  eg: "
