#: ../daemon/guestfsd.pod:81
msgid "This option is used to enable libguestfs live."
msgstr ""

#. type: textblock
#: ../daemon/guestfsd.pod:89
msgid ""
"The verbose flag is also set if the Linux command line contains the "
"substring C<guestfs_verbose=1>."
