#: ../docs/guestfs-faq.pod:853
msgid "The API has hundreds of methods, where do I start?"
msgstr ""

#. type: textblock
#: ../docs/guestfs-faq.pod:855
msgid ""
"We recommend you start by reading the API overview: L<guestfs(3)/API "
"OVERVIEW>."
msgstr ""

#. type: textblock
