"is included in libguestfs stable branches S<E<ge> 1.26.0>, S<E<ge> 1.24.6> "
"and S<E<ge> 1.22.8>, and also in RHEL S<E<ge> 7.0>.  Earlier versions of "
"libguestfs are not vulnerable."
