#. type: textblock
#: ../docs/guestfs-security.pod:274
msgid ""
"These two bugs in binutils affect the GNU L<strings(1)> program, and thus "
"the L</guestfs_strings> and L</guestfs_strings_e> APIs in libguestfs.  "
"Running strings on an untrusted file could cause arbitrary code execution "
"(confined to the libguestfs appliance)."
msgstr ""

