"C<root> is the filesystem root.  C<root> must not be NULL, use F</> instead."
msgstr ""

#. type: textblock
#: ../fish/guestfish-actions.pod:585 ../src/guestfs-actions.pod:875
msgid ""
"The flags are the same as the flags defined in E<lt>augeas.hE<gt>, the "
"logical I<or> of the following integers:"
msgstr ""

#. type: =item
#: ../fish/guestfish-actions.pod:591 ../src/guestfs-actions.pod:881
msgid "C<AUG_SAVE_BACKUP> = 1"
msgstr ""

#. type: textblock
#: ../fish/guestfish-actions.pod:593 ../src/guestfs-actions.pod:883
