msgstr ""

#. type: textblock
#: ../fuse/guestunmount.pod:53
msgid ""
"Now, when the write side of the pipe (ie. C<pipefd[1]>) is closed for any "
"reason, either explicitly or because the parent process exits, guestunmount "
"notices and unmounts the mountpoint."
