#. type: verbatim
#: ../v2v/virt-v2v.pod:714
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
" SLES 10        i586 with > 10GB of RAM: install 'kernel-bigsmp'\n"
"                i586 SMP: install 'kernel-smp'\n"
"                other i586: install 'kernel-default'\n"
